# Plan: Industry Agent Kit Framework (Complete)

## Overview

Build a reusable framework for creating industry-specific Cortex Agents grounded in Snowflake's **3 Core Pillars**:

| Pillar                         | Description                                   | Agent Kit Implementation              |
| ------------------------------ | --------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------- |
| **AI in Every Workflow**       | Intelligence embedded in tools teams use      | Surfacing options + Action tools      |
| **Business Logic and Context** | AI aligned with goals, rules, company context | Semantic views + VQRs + Orchestration |
| **Unified Data Foundation**    | Trusted, governed data from Horizon Catalog   | **Governance module** (optional)      |

