## New Skill: horizon-governance (Optional Module)

### Purpose

Add Horizon/governance capabilities to the agent as an optional module. When included, provides 4 tools:

### Governance Tools

| Tool                     | What It Does                       | Implementation                                   |
| ------------------------ | ---------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------ |
| **explain\_lineage**     | "Where does this data come from?"  | Query pipeline metadata, show RAW→GOLD flow      |
| **explain\_governance**  | "Why is this field masked?"        | Query masking/row policies, explain who set them |
| **check\_data\_quality** | "How fresh/reliable is this data?" | Show freshness, completeness, trust score        |
| **show\_access**         | "Who can access this data?"        | Query grants, roles, access history              |

